version_description: This is the official tab from the Doors.
This version differs from previous versions.  It has to the best of my ability, the correct chords, their chart and sequencing of the song.
This is the official tab from the Doors.
This version corrects some lyrics and chords, as well as the inclusion of some riffs.
I added the full song with the Am D sections and the rest of the lyrics.

This version contains chords and words for the entire song. It plays/reads more accurate to the chord progression of the cd version. The intro strumming is a bit tricky, as the transition from the A to a B is quick, but a good ear can pick out this quick change.
These are the original chords of the song taken from the 1970 album Morrison Hotel.
Revised the chords used in the intro and solos and also added 6th and 7th chords at end of verse and chorus.
